de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.judge

Class FinalJudgeBlackboardView

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.judge.FinalJudgeBlackboardView

  • public class FinalJudgeBlackboardView
extends java.lang.Object
    This view of the Blackboard is designed to be used by FinalJudge, therefore allowing remeasuring of ResourceDemandingInternalActions, SEFFBranches, and SEFFLoops.
